Dialogue: 0,0:00:18.99,0:00:25.90,apollon op,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,300)}{\blur3}You changed me so much I don't remember what I was like before we met.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:27.30,0:00:30.39,apollon op,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,300)}{\blur3}The breeze caresses our cheeks.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:30.39,0:00:32.50,apollon op,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,300)}{\blur3}Lullaby of Birdland...
Dialogue: 0,0:00:32.75,0:00:36.72,apollon op,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,300)}{\blur3}As we run down the slope,
Dialogue: 0,0:00:38.07,0:00:40.78,apollon op,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,300)}{\blur3}our flimsy shadows extend.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:40.78,0:00:45.72,apollon op,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,300)}{\blur3}It's like a neverending summer vacation.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:45.72,0:00:51.23,apollon op,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,300)}{\blur3}It feels like when we snuck into the pool.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:51.51,0:00:57.26,apollon op,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,300)}{\blur3}Yeah, let's swim with our clothes on. Jump in!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:57.61,0:00:59.95,apollon op,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,300)}{\blur3}It's an intense spiral of temptation.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:00.38,0:01:04.47,apollon op,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,300)}{\blur3}A beat pierces my heart. A strange one.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:04.96,0:01:08.04,apollon op,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,300)}{\blur3}It vanishes after a quick spark.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:08.16,0:01:10.84,apollon op,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,300)}{\blur3}Even on bad days, I dress up
Dialogue: 0,0:01:11.09,0:01:15.83,apollon op,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,300)}{\blur3}and dance to some swing. The music quickly surrounds me.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:15.83,0:01:18.68,apollon op,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,300)}{\blur3}What is this dance exactly? I can't stop it.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:18.68,0:01:27.94,apollon op,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,300)}{\blur3}Don't leave me. It's stuck in my head, and I can't get it out.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:29.34,0:01:31.03,apollon op,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,300)}{\blur3}The melody...
Dialogue: 0,0:01:34.79,0:01:36.82,apollon op,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,300)}{\blur3}is like love.
