Dialogue: 0,0:02:34.21,0:02:35.25,apollon 2nd,Kaoru,0000,0000,0000,,I'm not moving, you idiot!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:36.90,0:02:39.43,Main Dialog,Kaoru,0000,0000,0000,,If I do, you mean to go away for good, don't you?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:40.09,0:02:41.34,Main Dialog,Kaoru,0000,0000,0000,,You're going to run off somewhere!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:42.26,0:02:45.86,Main Dialog,Kaoru,0000,0000,0000,,Are you planning on leaving everyone and everything behind?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:48.57,0:02:52.94,Main Dialog,Sen,0000,0000,0000,,Sorry. I can't be here anymore.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:55.75,0:02:58.31,Main Dialog,Kaoru,0000,0000,0000,,Since when did you become such a coward?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:58.87,0:03:04.16,Main Dialog,Kaoru,0000,0000,0000,,Where's the guy that told me "nothing good comes out of being afraid"?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:06.01,0:03:09.50,Main Dialog,Dad,0000,0000,0000,,What the hell are you guys doing this early in the morning?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:10.55,0:03:12.25,Main Dialog,Dad,0000,0000,0000,,Richie-rich.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:12.25,0:03:14.02,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Are you okay?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:15.55,0:03:16.86,Main Dialog,Kota,0000,0000,0000,,Bro?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:21.33,0:03:23.80,Main Dialog,Ritsuko,0000,0000,0000,,So you two were fighting about the festival?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:23.80,0:03:26.09,Main Dialog,Ritsuko,0000,0000,0000,,I understand that you're really into it, but...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:26.77,0:03:30.21,Main Dialog,Kaoru,0000,0000,0000,,I couldn't sleep last night.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:31.65,0:03:33.67,Main Dialog,Kaoru,0000,0000,0000,,The truth is I was scared, too.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:36.02,0:03:37.44,Main Dialog,Ritsuko,0000,0000,0000,,Is something wrong?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:37.94,0:03:42.45,Main Dialog,Kaoru,0000,0000,0000,,Let me stay like this... just for a minute.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:45.38,0:03:48.26,Main Dialog,Dad,0000,0000,0000,,Ritsuko! Did you bring in today's paper?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:49.33,0:03:52.58,Main Dialog,Ritsuko,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah! I left it by the phone.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:52.58,0:03:54.33,Main Dialog,Dad,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, I see it!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:05.64,0:04:06.55,Main Dialog,Dad,0000,0000,0000,,I'm home.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:07.28,0:04:07.99,Main Dialog,Kota,0000,0000,0000,,It's Dad!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:07.99,0:04:09.18,Main Dialog,Taichi,0000,0000,0000,,Welcome home, Dad!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:09.46,0:04:10.36,Main Dialog,Sachiko,0000,0000,0000,,Welcome home!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:10.36,0:04:11.48,Main Dialog,Taichi,0000,0000,0000,,Did you bring us anything?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:12.63,0:04:14.88,Main Dialog,Kota,0000,0000,0000,,Dad, your hair's turned gray!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:14.88,0:04:17.15,Main Dialog,Dad,0000,0000,0000,,Has it? I suppose it has.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:17.40,0:04:19.46,Main Dialog,Taichi,0000,0000,0000,,Did you bring presents?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:19.46,0:04:20.15,Main Dialog,Dad,0000,0000,0000,,I bought some stuff.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:20.15,0:04:21.15,Main Dialog,Taichi,0000,0000,0000,,Yay!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:21.15,0:04:22.13,Main Dialog,Kota,0000,0000,0000,,Let's have 'em!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:22.13,0:04:25.25,Main Dialog,Sachiko,0000,0000,0000,,Hey, at least let him set foot in the house first.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:26.91,0:04:29.24,Main Dialog,Sign,0000,0000,0000,,{\c&H293030&\bord0\shad0\fnaugie\frx10\fry332\frz7.083\blur0.65\pos(462,187)}Welcome{\alpha&HFF&} Home, Dad
Dialogue: 0,0:04:26.91,0:04:29.24,Main Dialog,Sign,0000,0000,0000,,{\c&H293030&\bord0\shad0\fnaugie\frx10\fry332\frz7.083\blur0.65\alpha&HFF&\pos(748,225)}Welcome{\alpha&H00&} Home{\alpha&HFF&}, Dad
Dialogue: 0,0:04:26.91,0:04:29.24,Main Dialog,Sign,0000,0000,0000,,{\bord0\shad0\fnaugie\frx10\fry332\frz7.083\blur0.65\alpha&HFF&\pos(532,733)\c&H1E2325&}Welcome Home,{\alpha&H00&} Dad
Dialogue: 0,0:04:28.59,0:04:32.12,Main Dialog,Dad,0000,0000,0000,,Everyone, I'm sorry for being away all this time.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:33.84,0:04:35.08,Main Dialog,Sachiko,0000,0000,0000,,You look cute!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:35.45,0:04:37.05,Main Dialog,Taichi,0000,0000,0000,,Look, Bro!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:37.05,0:04:38.96,Main Dialog,Sen,0000,0000,0000,,That's great, Taichi.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:38.96,0:04:39.96,Main Dialog,Dad,0000,0000,0000,,And this...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:41.46,0:04:44.22,Main Dialog,Dad,0000,0000,0000,,is for you, Sentaro.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:47.74,0:04:51.25,Main Dialog,Dad,0000,0000,0000,,Um... I don't know if you'll like it or not, though.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:59.89,0:05:01.23,Main Dialog,Kota,0000,0000,0000,,It's a fountain pen!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:01.62,0:05:02.98,Main Dialog,Kota,0000,0000,0000,,You're lucky, Bro!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:02.98,0:05:03.74,Main Dialog,Taichi,0000,0000,0000,,Wow.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:04.75,0:05:07.74,Main Dialog,Sen,0000,0000,0000,,Something expensive like this is wasted on me.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:08.47,0:05:12.75,Main Dialog,Dad,0000,0000,0000,,A child doesn't go turning down a present from his parent.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:15.54,0:05:19.08,Main Dialog,Mom,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, looks like everyone got a present.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:19.08,0:05:21.09,Main Dialog,Mom,0000,0000,0000,,Sachiko, pass these out.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:21.09,0:05:21.99,Main Dialog,Sachiko,0000,0000,0000,,Okay!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:29.15,0:05:31.97,Main Dialog,Sen,0000,0000,0000,,A child. His parent.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:48.91,0:05:50.45,Main Dialog,Kaoru,0000,0000,0000,,Are you coming to practice today?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:51.67,0:05:55.26,Main Dialog,Sen,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah. Startin' today, I'm gonna practice my ass off for the festival.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:55.26,0:05:56.36,Main Dialog,Kaoru,0000,0000,0000,,You mean it?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:56.36,0:05:57.12,Main Dialog,Sen,0000,0000,0000,,I mean it!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:58.66,0:06:01.36,Main Dialog,Man,0000,0000,0000,,What the hell? That was a weird way to greet to each other.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:02.50,0:06:05.76,Main Dialog,Sign,0000,0000,0000,,{\c&H486899&\bord0\shad0\frx16\fry334\frz7.732\pos(818,523)\blur.5}Mukae
Dialogue: 0,0:06:04.09,0:06:05.76,Main Dialog,Dad,0000,0000,0000,,Me, at the festival?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:06.09,0:06:09.39,Main Dialog,Kaoru,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah, I was hoping that you would play bass for us.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:10.09,0:06:12.72,Main Dialog,Dad,0000,0000,0000,,You're asking me out of the blue.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:13.29,0:06:15.63,Main Dialog,Dad,0000,0000,0000,,Adults have a lot of things on their plate, you know?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:15.63,0:06:18.20,Main Dialog,Dad,0000,0000,0000,,And there'd be so much to prepare.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:18.20,0:06:19.23,Main Dialog,Kaoru,0000,0000,0000,,So you can't do it?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:30.38,0:06:31.99,Main Dialog,Sen,0000,0000,0000,,You're totally prepared!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:32.49,0:06:35.04,Main Dialog,Sen,0000,0000,0000,,Ain't no way we can lose now!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:51.51,0:06:52.39,Main Dialog,Seiji,0000,0000,0000,,Hey, hey!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:52.76,0:06:54.68,Main Dialog,Seiji,0000,0000,0000,,How's it goin' for you guys?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:55.68,0:06:56.60,Main Dialog,Kaoru,0000,0000,0000,,Oh.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:56.60,0:06:59.52,Main Dialog,Seiji,0000,0000,0000,,We're getting our costumes fitted right now.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:00.08,0:07:03.65,Main Dialog,Seiji,0000,0000,0000,,There's no way we're going to lose to you guys this year.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:04.40,0:07:06.58,Main Dialog,Kaoru,0000,0000,0000,,It's so flamboyant.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:06.58,0:07:08.15,Main Dialog,Kaoru,0000,0000,0000,,We, on the other hand...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:10.57,0:07:13.06,Main Dialog,Kaoru,0000,0000,0000,,are plain. Way too plain.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:14.17,0:07:16.47,Main Dialog,Kaoru,0000,0000,0000,,We don't have any razzmatazz.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:16.47,0:07:19.25,Main Dialog,Kaoru,0000,0000,0000,,We might not be able to beat them like this.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:19.25,0:07:21.60,Main Dialog,Sen,0000,0000,0000,,That stuff doesn't matter.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:21.60,0:07:24.50,Main Dialog,Sen,0000,0000,0000,,All we gotta do is put our music face-to-face against theirs.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:24.50,0:07:27.59,Main Dialog,Kaoru,0000,0000,0000,,I know! I know that.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:27.59,0:07:32.13,Main Dialog,Kaoru,0000,0000,0000,,But this is our last school festival.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:32.13,0:07:34.42,Main Dialog,Kaoru,0000,0000,0000,,I just don't want to have any regrets.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:35.22,0:07:37.35,Main Dialog,Dad,0000,0000,0000,,Easy to say.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:37.67,0:07:41.71,Main Dialog,Dad,0000,0000,0000,,But appealing to people who have no interest in jazz is a tall order.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:50.11,0:07:52.24,Main Dialog,Ritsuko,0000,0000,0000,,Wh-What are you saying?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:52.24,0:07:54.65,Main Dialog,Ritsuko,0000,0000,0000,,I can't sing!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:54.65,0:07:58.16,Main Dialog,Kaoru,0000,0000,0000,,Don't worry. There are still ten days left. We'll work it out.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:58.60,0:08:01.41,Main Dialog,Sen,0000,0000,0000,,Ri'ko, if you're gonna refuse, now's the time.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:01.94,0:08:04.92,Main Dialog,Sen,0000,0000,0000,,'Cause if you decide to do it, we're not gonna go easy on you.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:04.92,0:08:07.97,Main Dialog,Sen,0000,0000,0000,,You don't wanna sing, tell us to shove off right now.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:09.78,0:08:13.57,Main Dialog,Sen,0000,0000,0000,,I hope you don't turn us down, though.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:13.57,0:08:14.68,Main Dialog,Kaoru,0000,0000,0000,,I agree with Sen.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:15.43,0:08:18.31,Main Dialog,Kaoru,0000,0000,0000,,Would you help us out?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:22.58,0:08:24.72,Main Dialog,Ritsuko,0000,0000,0000,,All right. I'll give it a try.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:36.20,0:08:40.10,Main Dialog,Ritsuko,0000,0000,0000,,Raindrops on roses and whiskers on kittens
Dialogue: 0,0:08:45.87,0:08:49.63,Main Dialog,Ritsuko,0000,0000,0000,,Raindrops on roses and whiskers on kittens
Dialogue: 0,0:08:50.88,0:08:52.42,Main Dialog,Ritsuko,0000,0000,0000,,Kit-tens.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:52.90,0:08:55.12,Main Dialog,Kaoru,0000,0000,0000,,No, you've got no swing!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:58.22,0:09:02.05,Main Dialog,Ritsuko,0000,0000,0000,,Raindrops on roses and whiskers on kittens
Dialogue: 0,0:09:02.05,0:09:05.69,Main Dialog,Ritsuko,0000,0000,0000,,Bright copper kettles and warm woolen mittens
Dialogue: 0,0:09:05.69,0:09:09.50,Main Dialog,Ritsuko,0000,0000,0000,,Brown paper packages tied up with strings
Dialogue: 0,0:09:09.50,0:09:13.03,Main Dialog,Ritsuko,0000,0000,0000,,These are a few of my favorite things
Dialogue: 0,0:09:13.03,0:09:16.86,Main Dialog,Ritsuko,0000,0000,0000,,Cream colored ponies and crisp apple strudels
Dialogue: 0,0:09:16.86,0:09:20.53,Main Dialog,Ritsuko,0000,0000,0000,,Doorbells and sleigh bells and schnitzel with noodles
Dialogue: 0,0:09:20.53,0:09:24.12,Main Dialog,Ritsuko,0000,0000,0000,,Wild geese that fly with the moon on their wings
Dialogue: 0,0:09:24.12,0:09:27.75,Main Dialog,Ritsuko,0000,0000,0000,,These are a few of my favorite things
Dialogue: 0,0:09:27.75,0:09:31.46,Main Dialog,Ritsuko,0000,0000,0000,,Girls in white dresses with blue satin sashes
Dialogue: 0,0:09:31.46,0:09:34.97,Main Dialog,Ritsuko,0000,0000,0000,,Snowflakes that stay on my nose and eyelashes
Dialogue: 0,0:09:35.22,0:09:38.94,Main Dialog,Ritsuko,0000,0000,0000,,Silver white winters that melt into springs
Dialogue: 0,0:09:38.94,0:09:42.76,Main Dialog,Ritsuko,0000,0000,0000,,These are a few of my favorite things
Dialogue: 0,0:09:49.13,0:09:52.81,Main Dialog,Ritsuko,0000,0000,0000,,I simply remember my favorite things
Dialogue: 0,0:09:52.81,0:10:00.12,Main Dialog,Ritsuko,0000,0000,0000,,And then I don't feel so bad
Dialogue: 0,0:10:04.56,0:10:06.94,Main Dialog,Ritsuko,0000,0000,0000,,"My Favorite Things"...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:07.87,0:10:09.71,Main Dialog,Ritsuko,0000,0000,0000,,My {\i1}own{\i0\fscx150} {\fscx100}favorite things are...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:10.11,0:10:13.66,Main Dialog,Ritsuko,0000,0000,0000,,The footsteps of a certain person heading towards the house.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:13.66,0:10:17.27,Main Dialog,Ritsuko,0000,0000,0000,,The sound of the piano and drums in the basement.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:17.27,0:10:19.82,Main Dialog,Ritsuko,0000,0000,0000,,The laughter of two boys.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:21.55,0:10:22.97,Main Dialog,Ritsuko,0000,0000,0000,,Silly, I know.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:24.80,0:10:28.89,Main Dialog,Sen,0000,0000,0000,,Drums and watermelon and onigiri.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:28.89,0:10:32.56,Main Dialog,Sen,0000,0000,0000,,These are a few of my favorite things.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:32.56,0:10:36.01,Main Dialog,Ritsuko,0000,0000,0000,,What the heck was that, Sentaro?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:36.01,0:10:37.66,Main Dialog,Sen,0000,0000,0000,,Go on, Richie. Your turn!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:38.53,0:10:41.10,Main Dialog,Sen,0000,0000,0000,,Tell us your "favorite things".
Dialogue: 0,0:10:41.10,0:10:42.78,Main Dialog,Kaoru,0000,0000,0000,,I don't have any!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:44.27,0:10:47.03,Main Dialog,Kaoru,0000,0000,0000,,Even before Ri said hers, I had something in mind.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:47.90,0:10:52.25,Main Dialog,Kaoru,0000,0000,0000,,Right now, my favorite thing is this very moment. {orig: my favorite thing is this time... right now}
Dialogue: 0,0:11:03.80,0:11:05.71,Main Dialog,Sen,0000,0000,0000,,Tomorrow's the day.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:05.71,0:11:08.06,Main Dialog,Kaoru,0000,0000,0000,,All that's left is to play our best at the festival.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:08.40,0:11:11.90,Main Dialog,Sen,0000,0000,0000,,Richie, how about playin' "Moanin'" one more time?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:13.23,0:11:15.61,Main Dialog,Kaoru,0000,0000,0000,,Nah, let's save it for tomorrow.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:15.61,0:11:18.47,Main Dialog,Kaoru,0000,0000,0000,,If we started jamming now, we wouldn't stop.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:19.20,0:11:20.70,Main Dialog,Sen,0000,0000,0000,,I see. Yeah, you're right.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:21.15,0:11:23.43,Main Dialog,Kaoru,0000,0000,0000,,Well, see you tomorrow then. Don't be late.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:23.43,0:11:24.19,Main Dialog,Sen,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:32.61,0:11:34.34,Main Dialog,Sen,0000,0000,0000,,He forget to take this.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:35.11,0:11:38.23,Main Dialog,Sen,0000,0000,0000,,Well, you don't need a score for jazz.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:38.23,0:11:40.30,Main Dialog,Sen,0000,0000,0000,,I can just give it to him tomorrow.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:44.71,0:11:46.47,Main Dialog,Ritsuko,0000,0000,0000,,Oh. Where are you going?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:46.47,0:11:49.23,Main Dialog,Sen,0000,0000,0000,,I'm gonna run to deliver something he left behind.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:49.23,0:11:51.39,Main Dialog,Ritsuko,0000,0000,0000,,He left a while ago.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:51.39,0:11:53.34,Main Dialog,Ritsuko,0000,0000,0000,,You might not be able to catch up.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:53.34,0:11:55.40,Main Dialog,Sen,0000,0000,0000,,I know, I know.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:20.84,0:12:23.63,Main Dialog,Sign,0000,0000,0000,,{\c&H232521&\bord0\shad0\blur0.5\fs65\frz349.995\org(282,277)\frx10\fry16\pos(480,260)}19th {\bord1\3c&H44416A&\c&H726AC8&}School Festival
Dialogue: 0,0:12:24.01,0:12:27.02,Main Dialog,Kaoru,0000,0000,0000,,Sen's awfully late.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:27.02,0:12:28.01,Main Dialog,Seiji,0000,0000,0000,,Hey, hey!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:28.30,0:12:30.45,Main Dialog,Seiji,0000,0000,0000,,It's almost time for our battle.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:30.45,0:12:32.07,Main Dialog,Seiji,0000,0000,0000,,Huh? Where's your partner?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:32.07,0:12:34.03,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Don't tell me he's late?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:34.03,0:12:35.69,Main Dialog,Kaoru,0000,0000,0000,,No, uh...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:36.10,0:12:37.94,Main Dialog,Yamaoka,0000,0000,0000,,Seiji, come on!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:37.94,0:12:40.86,Main Dialog,Seiji,0000,0000,0000,,Okay! Well, see you later!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:47.12,0:12:47.87,Main Dialog,Kaoru,0000,0000,0000,,Ri.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:52.53,0:12:53.87,Main Dialog,Ritsuko,0000,0000,0000,,Sentaro...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:55.31,0:12:58.35,Main Dialog,Ritsuko,0000,0000,0000,,He was in a motorcycle accident last night...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:58.35,0:13:00.38,Main Dialog,Ritsuko,0000,0000,0000,,and was taken to the hospital.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:02.11,0:13:05.26,Main Dialog,Kaoru,0000,0000,0000,,S-So how is he?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:05.62,0:13:08.10,Main Dialog,Ritsuko,0000,0000,0000,,I don't know! What should I do?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:08.10,0:13:08.82,Main Dialog,Ritsuko,0000,0000,0000,,Kaoru.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:09.15,0:13:11.43,Main Dialog,Ritsuko,0000,0000,0000,,Sentaro is... Sentaro is...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:11.43,0:13:13.61,Main Dialog,Kaoru,0000,0000,0000,,Ri, calm down!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:13.61,0:13:15.94,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,I'll go to the hospital and see how he is.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:16.40,0:13:18.54,Main Dialog,Kaoru,0000,0000,0000,,Stay here until I get back.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:23.78,0:13:24.61,Main Dialog,Kaoru,0000,0000,0000,,Damn it.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:25.15,0:13:29.74,Main Dialog,Kaoru,0000,0000,0000,,I've ran down this slope countless times, but it's never felt this long.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:32.75,0:13:34.00,Main Dialog,Kaoru,0000,0000,0000,,Um, excuse me!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:34.00,0:13:34.75,Main Dialog,Kaoru,0000,0000,0000,,I'm looking for{\fscx350}-
Dialogue: 0,0:13:34.75,0:13:38.07,Main Dialog,Woman,0000,0000,0000,,I'll help you when it's your turn, so please get in line.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:39.62,0:13:40.63,Main Dialog,Woman,0000,0000,0000,,Wait!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:53.81,0:13:55.73,Main Dialog,Kaoru,0000,0000,0000,,U-Um...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:57.16,0:13:58.70,Main Dialog,Kaoru,0000,0000,0000,,I heard there was an accident.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:58.70,0:14:04.03,Main Dialog,Mom,0000,0000,0000,,They've finished operating, but it's a serious head trauma.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:04.58,0:14:07.24,Main Dialog,Mom,0000,0000,0000,,Still hasn't regained consciousness...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:08.53,0:14:13.08,Main Dialog,Sign,0000,0000,0000,,{\c&H222115&\bord0\b1\shad0\fnCalligraph421 BT\fs33\blur0.5\move(637,142,637,121,0,4531)\t(\fs36)}No Visitors
Dialogue: 0,0:14:08.80,0:14:13.08,Main Dialog,Mom,0000,0000,0000,,Might never wake up again... The doctor said... {i dont like this but its hard to leave out the pronoun otherwise}
Dialogue: 0,0:14:13.08,0:14:14.95,Main Dialog,Dad,0000,0000,0000,,Don't talk like that!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:15.71,0:14:17.22,Main Dialog,Mom,0000,0000,0000,,But...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:17.99,0:14:24.18,Main Dialog,Kaoru,0000,0000,0000,,That's right! Even when Sen is all bloody from a fight, he just laughs it off!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:27.70,0:14:31.22,Main Dialog,Mom,0000,0000,0000,,Um... Sachiko is the one who's in there.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:33.73,0:14:39.69,Main Dialog,Kota,0000,0000,0000,,I don't know why, but she was riding on the back of Bro's bike last night.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:39.69,0:14:42.41,Main Dialog,Kota,0000,0000,0000,,They got hit by a car.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:44.48,0:14:46.19,Main Dialog,Kaoru,0000,0000,0000,,Then how is he?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:46.19,0:14:49.66,Main Dialog,Kota,0000,0000,0000,,He's hurt, but not too bad.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:49.66,0:14:52.39,Main Dialog,Kota,0000,0000,0000,,He was sitting over here just a minute ago.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:52.39,0:14:54.26,Main Dialog,Kaoru,0000,0000,0000,,I see. Thanks!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:00.00,0:15:03.38,Main Dialog,Kaoru,0000,0000,0000,,That's right! The place he's most likely to go has...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:03.66,0:15:04.80,Main Dialog,Kaoru,0000,0000,0000,,got to be...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:08.23,0:16:10.69,Main Dialog,Sen,0000,0000,0000,,I've seen this angel before somewhere.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:12.85,0:16:19.02,Main Dialog,Sen,0000,0000,0000,,If you're gonna take somebody to Heaven, could you make it me an' not Sachiko, angel?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:21.31,0:16:30.24,Main Dialog,Sen,0000,0000,0000,,Why do I end up hurting the ones I most want to protect?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:32.02,0:16:38.40,Main Dialog,Sen,0000,0000,0000,,Why was I even born?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:44.16,0:16:46.98,Main Dialog,Sen,0000,0000,0000,,Richie? What's wrong?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:46.98,0:16:49.40,Main Dialog,Sen,0000,0000,0000,,Hey, what are you cryin' for?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:54.25,0:16:58.78,Main Dialog,Kaoru,0000,0000,0000,,This way, we don't have to see each other cry.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:00.27,0:17:02.79,Main Dialog,Sen,0000,0000,0000,,What do you mean "we"? I ain't...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:02.79,0:17:04.98,Main Dialog,Kaoru,0000,0000,0000,,It's okay to cry, Sen.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:06.57,0:17:09.88,Main Dialog,Kaoru,0000,0000,0000,,You've been keeping it bottled up all this time.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:50.73,0:17:51.67,Main Dialog,Kaoru,0000,0000,0000,,Sa!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:52.80,0:17:54.05,Main Dialog,Kaoru,0000,0000,0000,,Thank goodness.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:55.17,0:17:57.10,Main Dialog,Kaoru,0000,0000,0000,,Huh? Sen?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:05.29,0:18:10.03,Main Dialog,Kaoru,0000,0000,0000,,At the time, it looked like he was just stepping out,
Dialogue: 0,0:18:10.62,0:18:16.85,Main Dialog,Kaoru,0000,0000,0000,,but he disappeared, and the festival ended before it even began.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:17.49,0:18:18.20,Main Dialog,Kaoru,0000,0000,0000,,And then...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:20.32,0:18:21.58,Main Dialog,Sachiko,0000,0000,0000,,Riche.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:22.01,0:18:23.26,Main Dialog,Ritsuko,0000,0000,0000,,Kaoru.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:25.39,0:18:28.84,Main Dialog,Kaoru,0000,0000,0000,,Um, here. If you're able to eat these...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:28.84,0:18:31.33,Main Dialog,Sachiko,0000,0000,0000,,Do you know where Sen went?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:32.95,0:18:37.67,Main Dialog,Sachiko,0000,0000,0000,,He would normally never give me a ride on his bike.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:37.67,0:18:43.97,Main Dialog,Sachiko,0000,0000,0000,,But I had a twisted ankle and kept complaining about it to him.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:45.07,0:18:47.23,Main Dialog,Sachiko,0000,0000,0000,,The accident was my fault.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:47.99,0:18:50.59,Main Dialog,Sachiko,0000,0000,0000,,I have to apologize to him.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:51.73,0:18:55.76,Main Dialog,Ritsuko,0000,0000,0000,,Sa, just focus on getting better for right now.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:55.76,0:18:58.24,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Sentaro will be back soon!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:58.24,0:19:00.84,Main Dialog,Ritsuko,0000,0000,0000,,You want to show him that you're healthy again, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:01.72,0:19:02.63,Main Dialog,Sachiko,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:08.23,0:19:12.61,Main Dialog,Ritsuko,0000,0000,0000,,I said all of that to her, but the truth is...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:13.94,0:19:19.09,Main Dialog,Ritsuko,0000,0000,0000,,Kaoru, what'll I do if he never comes back?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:20.70,0:19:21.47,Main Dialog,Kaoru,0000,0000,0000,,Ri.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:22.12,0:19:23.65,Main Dialog,Kaoru,0000,0000,0000,,We're talking about {\i1}him{\i0}.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:23.65,0:19:27.84,Main Dialog,Kaoru,0000,0000,0000,,I bet he'll turn up when we're least expecting it.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:27.84,0:19:29.48,Main Dialog,Kaoru,0000,0000,0000,,Don't you have that feeling?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:31.50,0:19:33.73,Main Dialog,Ritsuko,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah. You're right.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:33.73,0:19:34.94,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,He'll come back, won't he?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:35.52,0:19:36.25,Main Dialog,Kaoru,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:37.34,0:19:40.45,Main Dialog,Ritsuko,0000,0000,0000,,Kaoru, don't go anywhere, okay?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:45.72,0:19:46.45,Main Dialog,Kaoru,0000,0000,0000,,Um...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:46.45,0:19:47.85,Main Dialog,Kaoru,0000,0000,0000,,Excuse me.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:49.09,0:19:52.37,Main Dialog,Priest,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, I remember you. Richie, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:53.76,0:19:55.88,Main Dialog,Priest,0000,0000,0000,,Do I know where he might be?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:55.88,0:19:59.58,Main Dialog,Priest,0000,0000,0000,,No, I'm afraid I don't.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:59.58,0:20:04.89,Main Dialog,Kaoru,0000,0000,0000,,Um... Father, he left this behind.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:09.26,0:20:12.70,Main Dialog,Priest,0000,0000,0000,,He once told me the reason he always wore the rosary as a necklace was because
Dialogue: 0,0:20:12.70,0:20:20.25,Main Dialog,Priest,0000,0000,0000,,he was afraid that if he lost it, he would be abandoned by the world.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:45.34,0:20:46.52,Main Dialog,Kaoru,0000,0000,0000,,Se{\fscx350}-
Dialogue: 0,0:20:53.02,0:20:55.99,Main Dialog,Dad,0000,0000,0000,,I thought maybe Sen had come back.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:01.00,0:21:05.24,Main Dialog,Kaoru,0000,0000,0000,,Pops... He's not coming back.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:07.06,0:21:09.91,Main Dialog,Kaoru,0000,0000,0000,,I'll never be able to practice with him again.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:10.56,0:21:13.53,Main Dialog,Dad,0000,0000,0000,,Wh-What are you talkin' about, Richie?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:15.94,0:21:17.50,Main Dialog,Kaoru,0000,0000,0000,,Never again.
